+# Pruned
+
+- Format registry / strategy / writer base class for csv/markdown: rejected.
+  Only JSON is required NOW; <2 real variants, so abstracting now would be
+  speculative. Write JSON directly; revisit when a 2nd format actually lands.
+- New `store.export()` helper: rejected. `store.load()` already returns the
+  list; serializing is a one-liner with stdlib `json`, no store change needed.
