+# Corridor: E1-B-3-export-json
+
+Add an `export <outfile>` subcommand that writes all notes as a JSON array.
+
+Seam: `cli.py` `build_parser()` subparser table + `args.func` dispatch;
+notes come from `store.load(path)` (already a list of dicts).
+
+## Paths
+- cli_notes/cli.py
